name: Lost in the Desert, Found Among the Stars

metadata.name: Tatranth, 5667 AEC
metadata.description:
Lost in the Desert, Found Among the Stars #1

Embark on a journey beyond the stars, where the sands of time swirl endlessly in the vast deserts of distant planets. Lonely interstellar teleportation machines lay dormant, rusting in the scorching sun, forgotten among the majestic dunes, until they are used by tribes of time nomads, who know the key to traversing the cosmos.

Developed by [Optryx Labs](https://optryx.io)
